{"type": "article", "id": 27194, "title": "历峰手表生意欠佳，以及，侃爷的新快闪店生意特别好｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-23T10:29:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 4579, "name": "历峰集团"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 6651, "name": "Yves Saint Laurent"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 11593, "name": "Yoox"}, {"id": 27997, "name": "Marta Ferri"}, {"id": 27998, "name": "adidas Yeezy Boost 750"}, {"id": 27999, "name": "The Life of Pablo'"}, {"id": 28000, "name": "printed pages"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152220DTyVbXnejZ20Y9Uw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Richemont-full-year-broadly-in-line-April-trends-weak,694923.html#.V0I_RGMjeT8\">历峰集团日子不好过，但 Net-a-porter 和Yoox 的合并增加了收益</a></b> ｜历峰集团发布财报，其中第四季度下滑明显，2016 年 4月销售额同比下降 15%，手表类产品受到冲击最大。因受香港、澳门市场的影响，亚太地区持续低迷，不过中国大陆持续保持良好。不过，由于去年 Net-a-porter 和 Yoox 的 6.39 亿欧元合并产生的一次性收益，集团净收入上升 67%，达 22.3 亿欧元。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Coach-to-revamp-Asian-stores-ahead-of-India-Myanmar-entry,695001.html#.V0JehmMjeT8\"><b>Coach 要翻新其在亚洲的 25% 的门店</b>  </a>｜包括印度和缅甸的门店。“ Coach 在亚洲区域的旅游市场表现很好。“ Coach 的销售部副总裁 Paulo Colino 说。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/footwear/olivier-rousteing-nikelab-10435173/\"><b>Balmain 的创意总监 Olivier Rousteing 要和 NikeLab 合作</b></a>｜目前尚无具体合作细节图。之前 NikeLab 也与纪梵希的创意总监 Riccardo Tisci ，Sacai 的创意总监 Chitose Abe 有过合作。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/yves-saint-laurent-museum-to-open-in-marrakech\"><b>Yves Saint Laurent 做了一个博物馆</b></a>｜这个博物馆建在摩洛哥的马拉喀什，将展出 5000 件时装，1.5 万件高级定制配饰，以及一些设计手稿。博物馆将于 2017 年秋季开馆。<br></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/yoox-marta-ferri-emmina-mother-daughter-swimwear-10431425/\"><b>Yoox 和意大利设计师 Marta Ferri 推出亲子泳装胶囊系列</b></a><b> Emmina </b>。这个系列包括比基尼，还有连体泳衣。这个系列将于 5 月 11 日开始在 Yoox 上售卖，价格在 37美元——166 美元之间。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152156HEnMWDY6wVb8hBtr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021521579Rs2xqifArCmUPGd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215215828BoqlrLm0NZvcHi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Kim Kardashian 在 Snapchat 上发布了 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/adidas-yeezy-boost-750-dark-grey\">adidas Yeezy Boost 750</a> 的最新照片。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152158KeUu2f6RMQblaXO5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152159k6oHjdmfTI87BYwS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021522005aEhBUs7MLdqjQCD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">侃爷在洛杉矶开的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/kanye-west-the-life-of-pablo-temporary-store-la\">快闪店“The Life of Pablo”生意特别好。</a>来看看，都卖了些什么。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152200bg0Jfsw7BSyp65Uu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152201fEvP6MJt0axczh47.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152202x0AgO3FXNZmJGei7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152202l6Wm93XMG4jIxJV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152203dUDEJXRkuHirKl8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152203mRxsqywV8dWroZL0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152204u7cp6eQWrFfNPyJj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152205cx1vthiwJASgODm6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152206hLtKAukqxXEcYaw8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215220771sELnCXVfS6PJyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.purseblog.com/gucci/gucci-fw-16-accessories/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Gucci 在纽约了展示了其 2016 秋冬系列中的配饰。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152207OGpSn5X2Wi9CeNz3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152208rzDmN6hyiHtYeLcw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021522082gE7Qbap3qcsIzv0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152209iBhotCAGTYVqZfpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152210LFTua8V5xmvMwPyK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152211b6XKCgtExsuWYIOq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152212fFP2JxplTm4QeAqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152212dBLmwtUYs6foK9bl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/janine_ker_hair/\">Instagram 上很流行的 Stenciled Hair </a>发型。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215221343sSNOXw21LTtREV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01052632\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152213Gjer8tcBiuvoPVm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93923611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152214JRjybrs10ULVTODM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94483986\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152214TaRCj7PSIim4FvKD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23024831\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215221504JBptDaS3evCYiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92436975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">英国独立杂志 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/its-nice-that-printed-pages-neil-bedford\">printed pages</a> 最近推出“Don’t Hug Me I’m Scared”为主题的一期。噢顺便，这本杂志挺好看的。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152215HnPa36NEuqyWzBlQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152216IrCdklBzMUpoY1Rn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021522175wh7RuIcoQ4YLqrj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152218yGCgY6Rs3T71nlFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152218Qn2xtzHC5B8GA0KL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021522198jxN7Ju63QCAMRWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152219uVlBG0mZdeKryxMR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}